Release Notes:


Based on the actual incident that rocked California's legal system, 
Changeling tells the shocking tale of a mother's quest to find her 
son, and those who won't stop until they silence her. In addition 
to directing, Clint Eastwood provides what may be his most 
beautiful, touching and compelling score. Clint Eastwood directs 
Angelina Jolie and John Malkovich in a provocative thriller based 
on actual events: Changeling. In the film, Christine Collins' 
(Jolie) prayers are met when her kidnapped son is returned. But 
amidst the frenzy of the photo op reunion, she realizes this child 
is not hers. Facing corrupt police and a skeptical public, she 
desperately hunts for answers,only to be confronted by a truth 
that will change her forever.
